and it was 100 times harder than an enchanter. My enchanter at 43 could kill <br>
10 giants in 10 minutes. My 50 rogue couldn't kill one. Sure, sure, <br>
solo'ing is not a measure of power. Then what is? My rogue has died to a <br>
green that jumped him in the dreadland tunnel. I still see rogues shouting <br>
for groups, post 50, pre 50, etc. This game was built to level a caster and <br>
twink a melee for fun. That's not a horrible thing, I just wish it said <br>
that on the box. <br>
